Package: flo
Version: 1.3
Section: finance
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: thatspeedykid <https://github.com/thatspeedykid/flo>
Description: flo — simple budget app
 A free, open source personal finance app.
 Monthly budgets, debt snowball, net worth tracking,
 event planning and split cost calculator.
 100% offline. No accounts, no cloud, no ads.
Homepage: https://github.com/thatspeedykid/flo
